General Info
///////////////////
The App has been developed and tested using:
Mobile phone: Mi A2 Lite
Android version: 9


Assumptions
///////////////////
> "In case the user watches 4 videos, the app should display an interstitial ad in one of the following scenarios",
    meaning, in case user watches 4 videos during the whole interval of 12 hours, not necessarily in a row.
> re-watching an ad again does not consider to be another ad play.
> There might a delay with the interstitial ad for the sake of loading


Missing
///////////////////
> App OOP architecture
    View and modules. Including
    -IronSourceLibraryWrapper
    -AdvertisingManager
    -RewardedVideo
> Data binding for ad display button (enable/disable), and rewards amount.
